data.name: ClientKeyTitle
data.value: Key that was generated on device, but was changed due to the collision with existing interview on server

data.name: Tooltip_Filter_Assignment
data.value: Assignment ID. Click in the field to type the full ID number.

data.name: Tooltip_Filter_Questionnaire
data.value: Select a questionnaire to see its associated interviews in the list. Select “All questionnaires” to see interviews associated with any questionnaire.

data.name: Tooltip_Filter_Responsible
data.value: User responsible. Click in the field to choose a user name either by selecting it directly or typing to filter the list of user names further.

data.name: Tooltip_Filter_Status
data.value: Status of interview. Select a status to see all interviews with that status. Select “All statuses” to see interviews with any status.

data.name: Tooltip_Table_Assignment
data.value: Identifier for the assignment to which this interview belongs. Click on the sort icon to sort by assignment number.

data.name: Tooltip_Table_HideShowIdentifying
data.value: Click here to hide or show the identifying questions. Hiding identifying questions may provide more space for other information. Showing identifying questions may provide details for differentiating between interviews.

data.name: Tooltip_Table_IdentifyingQuestions
data.value: Information that identifies each assignment. These are the answers to questions marked as identifying in Designer.

data.name: Tooltip_Table_InterviewKey
data.value: Short case identifier that appears throughout the system--in Headquarters, Supervisor, and Interviewer. Consider using this ID when communicating with field team, rather than a large set of identifying question.

data.name: Tooltip_Table_LastUpdate
data.value: When changes to the interview were last posted to the server. Click on the sort icon to sort by time.

data.name: Tooltip_Table_ReceivedByInterviewer
data.value: Indicator for whether the interview has been downloaded onto the interviewer’s tablet. Click on the sort icon to sort by receipt by the interviewer.

data.name: Tooltip_Table_Responsible
data.value: User currently responsible for the assignment. Click sort icon to sort user name.

data.name: Tooltip_Table_Status
data.value: Status of the interview in the survey workflow. Click on the sort icon to sort by status.

data.name: Tooltip_Table_ErrorsCount
data.value: Shows total number of invalid questions and static texts in the interview. Multiple failed validation conditions on same entity are counted as 1.
